sequenceDiagram
    actor U as Premium User
    participant FE as React<br/>ReportsPage
    participant API as DRF<br/>GenerateReportView
    participant SER as GenerateReportSerializer
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    U->>FE: Select report type, date range, click "Generate"
    FE->>API: POST /api/reports/ {type: "security", date_from, date_to}
    API->>SER: GenerateReportSerializer.validate(data)
    SER-->>API: Validated parameters
    API->>DB: Alert.objects.filter(timestamp__range=[from, to])
    DB-->>API: Alert data for period
    API->>API: Aggregate statistics, generate summary
    API->>DB: Report.objects.create(type, data, generated_by=user)
    DB-->>API: Report instance
    API-->>FE: 201 Created {report_id, type, generated_at}
    FE-->>U: Report added to report list
